Introduction

H2L (Korean: 에이치투엘; Japanese: エイチトゥエル) was a three-member girl group under Regolith Entertainment. They made their official debut on January 16, 2017 with their first digital single "Winter Story" but disbanded on May 26, 2017.Their group name was taken from the initial of the second hangul of their names: Sanha, Yuli and Hwilyn.
